cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "EYE-LEAN (Locomotion, Exploration, Action and Navigation with Eye Tracking): a Behavioral Research Toolkit for Data Rich Virtual Reality Experiments"
message: "If you use Eye_lean in research, please cite this toolkit and the underlying algorithms (LHIPA: Duchowski 2018; RIPA2: Jayawardena 2025)."
type: software
